```

---

# 🌟 4. Wildcards vs Regex (Important Difference)

| Feature | Wildcards | Regex (`grep`) |
| ------- | --------- | -------------- |
| Usage   | Filenames | File content   |
| `*`     | any chars | `.*`           |
| `?`     | one char  | `.`            |
| `[abc]` | same      | same           |

